&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for an Account Executive to support market development of net new or acquisition revenue, while also expanding current accounts. This role will be focused on Junior Colleges in the Northeast region of the United States.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To succeed, you’ll:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own a sales cycle.&lt;/strong&gt; You’ll collaborate with commissioners, athletic directors and coaches to ensure their schools and teams have what they need to develop and improve.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Close sales on the phone and through online demos.&lt;/strong&gt; We believe the more calls and demos you make, the more sales you make.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work across multiple sports.&lt;/strong&gt; Whether it’s global football or American football, you’ll know how every team can benefit from video analysis. Understanding our customer personas regardless of sport is extremely important.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Travel&lt;/strong&gt;. You&#39;ll occasionally visit your territory to be on the front lines with prospective customers (which happens to be one of our company values).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
