&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be a visual and verbal storyteller&lt;/strong&gt;. You’ll craft and communicate compelling concepts that are forward-facing, differentiated, and relevant to customer and business needs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
